				<li><a href="HappyBirthdayFogcam/">Golden Gate [X]press 10th Anniversary of Fogcam</a>&nbsp;(archived version)</li>
			</ul>

			<p>FogCam! created by Jeff Schwartz (aka Webdog)&nbsp;and Dan Wong (aka Danno).<BR>Operated by <a href="https://at.sfsu.edu">Academic Technology<a> at San Francisco State University. <P> Danno still has some amusing <a href="http://danwong.org/gallery.html">1995 FogCam pictures</a> on his website. </P><a href="http://www.twitter.com/FogCam">Follow us on Twitter</a>.</p>

